@startuml DailyDangerousClassification_MainFlow
title Daily Dangerous Classification - Main Flow

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam titleFontSize 16
skinparam titleFontStyle bold

|JobService|
start
:POST /api/classificationJobs/scanningDailyDangerousClassification;
note right
  Parameters:
  - batchSize: Batch size for external push
  - isLicensee: Process Licensee or Credit customers
  
  Ex: batchSize = 5000, isLicensee = true
end note

:Execute(batchSize, isLicensee);

:Prepare push parameters;
note right
  **PushDataToExternalEntity**:
  - RoleGroup: Member
  - ExternalBatchSize: batchSize
  - IsUpdateDangerToMainDB: true
  - IsWriteLog: from appSettings
  - ServiceName: "DailyDangerousClassificationJobService"
end note

|Do-While Loop|
note right
  **Pagination Loop**:
  Continue until all dangerous customers processed
  Separate tracking for Licensee vs Credit
end note

repeat
  |Service Layer|
  :GetDangerousClassification(isLicensee);
  note right
    **Get Dangerous Customers**:
    - FROM DangerousDetection table
    - WHERE IsLicensee = @isLicensee
    - AND CustID > LastCustID (pagination)
    - AND ClassifiedDate > LastScannedDate
    - AND ClassifiedScore > Threshold
    - ORDER BY CustID
    
    **Source**: AI/ML Detection System ⭐
    
    **System Parameters** (based on isLicensee):
    - Deposit: DangerousScoreClassification_Deposit_*
    - Credit: DangerousScoreClassification_Credit_*
    
    **Returns**:
    - DangerousCCLastScanned:
      * LastCustID (pagination)
      * LastScannedDate (pagination)
    - DangerousCCs[]:
      * CustID, CTSCustID
      * CategoryID, CategoryGroup
      * ClassifiedScore, ClassifiedDate
      * SubscriberID, RoleID
  end note

  :Check isContinue;
  note right
    **Continue Condition**:
    isContinue = (LastCustID > 0)
    
    - LastCustID > 0: More customers to process
    - LastCustID = 0: All done
  end note

  if (isContinue?) then (yes)
    |Service Layer|
    :Transform to PA entities;
    note right
      **DangerousToCCEntity → InsertProblemAccountEntity**:
      
      For each dangerous customer:
      {
        CustID: x.CustID,
        CTSCustID: x.CTSCustID,
        RoleID: x.RoleID,
        SubscriberID: x.SubscriberID,
        CategoryID: x.CategoryID,
        CategoryGroupID: x.CategoryGroup,
        IsLicensee: isLicensee,
        CreatedBy: StarixITId,
        Remark: "",
        IsMarkedDirectly: null,
        **IsFromAI: true**, ⭐
        IsFromCTS: false,
        IsFromTVS: false,
        IsFromTW: false
      }
      
      **Key Flag**: IsFromAI = true
      Indicates AI/ML detection source
    end note

    :Chunk by externalBatchSize;
    note right
      Split into batches for processing
      Batch size from push parameters
    end note

    repeat
      :Process chunk;
      
      :InsertProblemAccountPackage();
      note right
        **Insert PA Classification**:
        - FunctionId: DailyDangerousClassification
        - CCInputFlow: Potential
        - Insert into CTSCustomerClassification
        - Apply PA rules and logic
        - Returns: Inserted CustIDs
        
        **Inherited Method** from ProblemAccountServices
      end note

      :PushExternalPackageByCustId();
      note right
        **Push to MainDB** (External):
        - Input: Inserted CustIDs
        - Parameters: paras (push parameters)
        - Makes dangerous classification visible
        - Batch push for efficiency
      end note

    repeat while (More chunks?) is (yes)
    -> no;

    |System Parameters|
    :Update LastCustID;
    note right
      **Update System Parameter**:
      - If isLicensee = true:
        Key: DangerousScoreClassification_Deposit_LastCustID
      - If isLicensee = false:
        Key: DangerousScoreClassification_Credit_LastCustID
      
      Value: dangerousCCs.LastCustID
    end note

    :Update LastScannedDate;
    note right
      **Update System Parameter**:
      - If isLicensee = true:
        Key: DangerousScoreClassification_Deposit_LastScannedDate
      - If isLicensee = false:
        Key: DangerousScoreClassification_Credit_LastScannedDate
      
      Value: dangerousCCs.LastScannedDate
    end note
  else (no)
    note right
      **No more dangerous customers**:
      All processed for current customer type
    end note
  endif

repeat while (isContinue = true?) is (yes)
-> no;

|JobService|
:Complete;
note right
  **Job Completion**:
  All dangerous customers processed
  for selected customer type (Licensee or Credit)
  
  **Separate Runs**:
  - Run 1: isLicensee = true (Deposit customers)
  - Run 2: isLicensee = false (Credit customers)
end note

stop

note bottom
  **Key Characteristics**:
  
  1. **AI/ML Detection Source** ⭐:
     - Dangerous score calculated by ML models
     - Automated classification
     - IsFromAI = true flag
  
  2. **Separate Licensee vs Credit**:
     - Two separate job runs
     - Independent pagination tracking
     - Different system parameters
  
  3. **Do-While Loop**:
     - Simple loop structure
     - Continues until LastCustID = 0
     - Pagination via system parameters
  
  4. **Batch Processing**:
     - Chunk by externalBatchSize
     - Insert PA + Push to MainDB per chunk
     - Optimized external push
  
  5. **Data Transformation**:
     - DangerousToCCEntity → InsertProblemAccountEntity
     - Set IsFromAI = true (AI detection marker)
     - Set CreatedBy = StarixITId
  
  6. **External Push**:
     - Push to MainDB after each chunk
     - Makes dangerous classification visible
     - Enables external monitoring
  
  7. **Inheritance**:
     - Extends ProblemAccountServices
     - Reuses InsertProblemAccountPackage method
     - Consistent PA insertion logic
end note

@enduml

